import app from './app'
import './database'
app.listen(4000);
console.log('server listen on port',4000)

import mongoose from "mongoose";

mongoose.connect("mongodb://Localhost/companydb")
.then(db=>console.log('Db is connected'))
.catch(error=>console.log(error))
